LIST OF MOST - FOLLOWED INSTAGRAM ACCOUNTS
This list contains the top 50 accounts with the most followers on the social photo - sharing platform Instagram .
As of December 2018 , the most followed user is Instagram 's own account , with over 270 million followers .
Cristiano Ronaldo is the most followed individual , with over 148 million followers .
13 accounts have exceeded 100 million followers on the site .
